{"cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "status": "NEW", "cf_tracking_firefox60": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox61": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox62": "---", "creator": "jh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de", "mentors_detail": [], "depends_on": [], "cf_status_firefox_esr60": "---", "cf_user_story": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_relnote": "---", "platform": "All", "cf_status_firefox58": "wontfix", "cf_status_firefox59": "wontfix", "keywords": ["regression", "testcase"], "cf_status_firefox57": "wontfix", "summary": "Font inflation layout regression", "cf_last_resolved": null, "attachments": [{"creator": "jh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [], "content_type": "text/html", "id": 8940557}, {"creator": "jh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [], "content_type": "image/png", "id": 8940558}], "votes": 0, "classification": "Components", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "---", "comment_count": 4, "comments": [{"text": "Created attachment 8940557\nTestcase extracted from the footnote box on the bottom\n\nSTR:\nUsing Firefox for Android, enable Settings -> Accessibility -> Use system font size to enable font inflation for desktop pages and then visit http://www.hirezfox.com/km/co/co1024/d/20171227.html\n\nThe layouting of the heading above the comic and of the footnote boxes at the bottom will appear broken - the font size of those elements has increased, but the line spacing of those elements hasn't. At least for me, the effect on the footnote boxes also gets worse if the page loads from the cache as opposed to the first load from the network. (And opening that tab in the dev tools Inspector via WebIDE fixes things again)\n\nThe regression range I found is https://hg.mozilla.org/integration/mozilla-inbound/pushloghtml?fromchange=e6e712904806da25a9c8f48ea4533abe7c6ea8f4&tochange=d6bf703c5deaf1e328babd03d5e68ff2a4ffe10e, so most likely bug 1308876.", "author": "jh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de", "id": 12949920, "time": "2018-01-08T00:32:38Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8940558\nScreenshot_20180108-013001.png", "author": "jh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de", "id": 12949921, "time": "2018-01-08T00:33:31Z"}, {"text": "(In reply to Jan Henning [:JanH] from comment #0)\n> At least for me,\n> the effect on the footnote boxes also gets worse if the page loads from the\n> cache as opposed to the first load from the network. (And opening that tab\n> in the dev tools Inspector via WebIDE fixes things again)\n\nPresumably because if the images load somewhat slower from the network as opposed to getting them quickly from the cache, they trigger another reflow or something of the content below them?", "author": "jh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de", "id": 12951480, "time": "2018-01-08T08:36:56Z"}, {"text": "(I can reproduce in Nightly on Android, FWIW.)", "author": "dholbert@mozilla.com", "id": 12952975, "time": "2018-01-08T19:44:42Z"}], "id": 1428670, "priority": "P3", "cc": ["dholbert@mozilla.com", "tnikkel@gmail.com"], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "56 Branch", "is_cc_accessible": true, "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": "---", "see_also": [], "cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr60": "---", "cf_platform_rel": "---", "product": "Core", "cf_fx_iteration": "---", "blocks": [1308876], "qa_contact": "", "creation_time": "2018-01-08T00:32:38Z", "cf_status_firefox_esr52": "unaffected", "component": "Layout", "assigned_to_detail": {"email": "nobody@mozilla.org", "id": 1, "name": "nobody@mozilla.org", "real_name": "Nobody; OK to take it and work on it"}, "cf_tracking_firefox_esr60": "---", "cf_status_firefox62": "affected", "cf_status_firefox61": "fix-optional", "cf_status_firefox60": "fix-optional", "target_milestone": "---", "cf_rank": null, "cf_qa_whiteboard": "", "severity": "normal", "groups": [], "cf_status_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "url": "http://www.hirezfox.com/km/co/co1024/d/20171227.html", "cf_status_thunderbird_esr60": "---", "creator_detail": {"email": "jh+bugzilla@butte